p.p: A subset of the SNOMED CT clinical terminology (i.e. coding system) intended for use in the UK, previously named SnomedCTUK, that describes the newborn blood spot screening result substatus.

p.strong: Any code from the SNOMED CT UK newborn blood spot screening result substatus subset with subset original id 61091000000138.
NB: This subset ID, 61091000000138, has not yet been defined in a release of SNOMED CT.
